-- Mondi, Bedrock Appeal South African Antitrust Ruling to Block Unit Merger
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-16T07:22:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/mondi-bedrock-appeal-south-african-antitrust-ruling-to-block-unit-merger.html

          
          
             Bedrock Mining Support and Mondi
Ltd. appealed a decision to block a merger that includes three
of Mondi’s hardwood timber plantations, South Africa’s antitrust
regulator said in an e-mailed statement today.  
 The appeal will be heard by the Competition Tribunal from
July 19 to 28, the Pretoria-based regulator said in an e-mailed
statement today.  
          
          


  


        